{"tid":299055,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜隨筆","createTime":"2017-06-26T18:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T14:49:05.000Z","uid":23378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab8041d730217d6715ecc63d971079c91756647","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/020751_1a152d8e8cb3471ee599187fbf8b4d2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F020751_1a152d8e8cb3471ee599187fbf8b4d2f.jpg&h=929d3765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我只是被黑夜吸掉那魂魄 剩下那空洞孤寂的空殻"},{"pid":"3ea3b2fdecf28f7e4574ccecd78891b2d99104f7","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"看著那迷離的夜空，甚麼星體、月亮的，都全不翼而飛。我，坐在家中陽台的一個角落，街燈暗淡的黃光映進天花，照亮了，我那蒼白無力的內心。可這種淡黃與日落的相比，絲毫沒有一點暖意。"},{"pid":"30479e16bc933291025ca6185bfe4cd7c9bb38a3","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"文筆唔太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果大家唔喜歡呢種表達手法 我可以改下<br />\n<br />\n比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡力改善 寫啲好文比大家"},{"pid":"604ad18f945ee612158982071f8fcb385788db30","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"「Wohoooo，無心睡眠，wohoooo，腦交戰，若是你在懷念昨天的你....」<br />\n睡不了，腦海中一直哼唱著張國榮的無心睡眠，心中浮現起那個她，那個不太願意再提的--她。"},{"pid":"dae49278f30cb8db82ad6d440bed20700173720b","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:25:40.000Z","msg":"心裡自是暗煩，明明都已是一段長時間了，她倒是不會對你再有任何攻擊性的，可為何想起了，就是一陣辛酸。<br />\n最近，心中這塊大石又再是顯得沉重，沒有甚麼緣故，亦沒任何理由。總之，那個她總是肆虐地不其然跑出來，在心深處略過，泛起一陣漣漪。"},{"pid":"02b4ad40ecd9ebd792ad6483deeeaa3faa85a61d","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"用力地呼出一口氣，算是在幻想中放倒了她。"},{"pid":"13445efd97542a48d7df5d1cb3f86b607af6d2d9","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:31:00.000Z","msg":"二時二十八分，這分鐘不太重要，沒有甚麼值得我記著的一分鐘，反正，就只有我獨自一人，依然坐在那泛著淡黃色的陽台角中。"},{"pid":"74cb56cb7bd7388f56ae4df094242115487a54fd","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:35:49.000Z","msg":"如果你問到，我為何會突然孤獨纏身，那我會說，因為我失眠。若然你問到，為何我會失眠，我會說，因為孤獨。<br />\n這是一個先有雞還是先有蛋的問題，我會說，why not both?我們是三為一體的，孤獨，失眠，我。加上黑夜作伴，是此刻的四大金剛。"},{"pid":"138f1c04f43085d9fb191b58c56b68646f7fdbd2","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:37:38.000Z","msg":"或許是標題不夠吸引，文體不夠獨到，似乎找不到半個讀者與我於此時此刻由文字訴苦。"},{"pid":"aaa44c2a26a316ec9da64102806e358a463a2c3d","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"就是這種情況，就是這種感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n才能稱得上，孤獨。"},{"pid":"82b139ee821fee1a6cf7e0c6ff881d962e8d778e","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:42:16.000Z","msg":"人生，總有歡喜。難免，亦常有淚。<br />\n我地大家，在獅子山.......我地？這邊除了我，還有誰？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喂</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喂</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">喂</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">喂</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">喂</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">喂</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">有</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">無</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">人</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">人</span>"},{"pid":"e317b1893bd96de01104eb9e8244cd756f7d9117","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:43:59.000Z","msg":"吞了一口水，算了吧，還是回睡房試著睡吧。"},{"pid":"6e5bac915d971c385a5230ea3cece091b6b08753","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T18:46:40.000Z","msg":"晚安了，各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa908c6462f2aeecde815b4678c47112f7e92573","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b76343a33e7bdd9de4967d0e64a59643c40e38","tid":299055,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:34:10.000Z","msg":"文筆幾好"},{"pid":"e0270614896bb5ce71ab66114ede3e006e0a904e","tid":299055,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"當有個平台發泄下情緒，都唔錯架。"},{"pid":"abdddd62f7bf5b5789e5e16af8e3906e6a23bd87","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T18:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文筆幾好</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為沉左底無人會睇"},{"pid":"5ee75ddfb357674c2de32e4cbdb744cbcb4751b1","tid":299055,"uid":23378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"2018年1月29日，半年過去了，今天的你 過得怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n轉換了新的工作，認識上新的朋友，也開始有新的緋聞了。可就是提不起幹勁去愛。<br />\n<br />\n難道沒練習太耐，感覺都追不回來，試圖再努力愛，也顯得不自在。<br />\n<br />\n並非為賦新詩強說愁，只是人大了，再看看一些舊作品，才知道，即使我身處的地方變得再不堪，總有些事是不會變，就是做人那份難。<br />\n<br />\n半年過後，不知我會身處何方，在看甚麼。只是...近幾天，她又再纏上我心。"}]}